type: Tutorial - Wanna Help? Come On In!

definition.text: Welcome to the Community! We are always excited to get more people on board, and truly appreciate your help!

paragraphs.text: Let me guess... You're a conscientious individual and want to give back as a token of appreciation for making Superalgos free and open-source! Or you're impressed with Superalgos and want to be a part of it! Or maybe you realize that Superalgos is the future of trading and want to jump on board before the ship sails!
Whatever your motivation may be, we want you in!
This is how you may get started!
